Options:
  Git Alias:
    newmain               Nuke local main & rebuild from remote
    pullmain              Switch to main & update local main from any branch
    newmaster             Nuke local master & rebuild from remote
    pullmaster            Switch to master & update local master from any branch
    deletebranches        Deletes all branches except main/master & current branch
    gco                   Checkout a branch
    gnew                  Checkout a new branch
    pr                    Cretae a pull request
    dpr                   Create a draft pull request
    view                  View current pull request in web browser

  React Alias:
    addts                 Add typescript to a project
    jstots                Change JavaScript files to typescript files
    tailwindnext          Create a new Next.js project with Tailwind

  Shell Alias:
    c                     Clear shell
    reload                Reload shell source

  TMUX Alias:
    tv                    Split TMUX windows verticaly
    th                    Split TMUX windows horizontally
    tkill                 Kill TMUX pane
    tstart                Start prefered TMUX window positioning

  Shell Alias:
    du -a /               Pretend to work

  Projects Alias:
    bc                    Jump to bc project
    tpag                  Jump to tpag project
    pm                    Jump to pm project

